snippet.title: (8-bit Remix) Bakamitai - Yakuza 0
snippet.description:
2a03 + MMC5 cover of Bakamitai from the Yakuza series.

A few days ago I made this as a birthday gift for Gabe Fern, an amazing pixel artist and dear friend. He got me into the Yakuza games, and it's been a blast playing through 0 and Kiwami! 

I tried making this a 2a03-only cover, but I struggled to make the chorus stand out, so I decided to add the MMC5 to power it up.

I hope you've enjoyed it :D

NSF: https://www.dropbox.com/s/56uae5858kt8as0/BAKAMITAI.nsf?dl=1

Bakamitai is composed by Mitsuharu Fukuyama, and is (C) Sega
Chiptune Arrangement by Saria Lemes a.k.a. pedipanol, using j0cc Famitracker.
Thumbnail Art by Gabe Fern.
Oscilloscope Visualization generated with Corrscope.
